Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,本宝宝带领你们继续前进\NOkay, so the next thing we want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这次来谈谈部署的问题\Nis talk about deployment for a little bit,
