Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,相反，你打包你的程序然后提交到商店里\NInstead, you package your app and you submit it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我们下节课要做的那样\Nto the Store, like we'll do in the next lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,用户到商店里获取你的应用\NSo, users will acquire your app from the Store
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,获取到一个我们称之为“App Package”的东西\Nas what's called an "App Package."
