Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去安装这个应用\Nin an app package to install the app
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,并且在你确认从你的设备上卸载应用时\Nand ensure that all traces of the app are gone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,保证你应用所有的痕迹都被清理掉\Nfrom the device whenever they choose to uninstall that app.
